Text: RE Lunchis at Louisiana your old Tennessee Building Is that the one on the tunnel level What time will we need to be there to get a seat That will be fine with me Ill let Danetta know Original Message From mailto Sent Friday July AM To Lisa Norwood Subject RE Lunch How about somewhere in between Wheres Danetta Maybe Treebeards in Interfirst Plaza Lisa Norwood on AM To cc Subject RE Lunch We havent set a place yet do you want to try Angelika in the Bayou place or meet somewhere closer in between I am at Louisiana Bank of America Original Message From mailto Sent Friday July AM To Lisa Norwood Subject Re Lunch Sounds great Phone number is Lisa Norwood on AM To cc Subject Lunch Michelle I am planning to meet Dannetta Beaushaw for lunch on Monday do you want to join us Lisa PS Whats your phone number again
